{"type": "article", "id": 63220, "title": "今日头条上线漫威冷知识挑战赛，雀巢要开一家“京味儿”快闪咖啡馆 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-04-24T04:44:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 38, "name": "电影"}, {"id": 981, "name": "社交媒体"}, {"id": 5880, "name": "今日头条"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190424122057j3TEGCufd7vKS0LX.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥 </h3><p line=\"9LIq\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/1271329254/4364210773720694\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>QQ 阅读在世界阅读日，宣布黄轩成为品牌代言人。</b></a>同时，QQ 阅读发起“与黄轩组队读书”活动，活动从 4 月 23 日至 4 月 27 日，每天会抽取用户送 1 天至 30 天不等的免费 QQ 阅读会员。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122249bgzrJB4QHnc2oXFq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"80Qo\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/6038290538/4363886113206568\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>摩拜单车在世界地球日推出环保家具产品。</b></a>它和 YUUE 产品设计工作室合作，把摩拜单车的报废零件回收改造，重新创作出躺椅、立式灯、茶几、桌面整理架、烛台 5 款家具用品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2019042412231574JsOTBMQN0h6yow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707733\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122315MdxUhAryGa3zJ8Yp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751566\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122315Dufj7624ZPx0QTqX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.356481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122316bzlytg2TVmRQ86Sa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"jAJK\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NDA5NTkwMA==&amp;mid=2660625264&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=452445417f70f6152f1c4d81334ff2a8&amp;chksm=bdedbd038a9a3415b2bc8c874b091d00b9e50e6248b338f8f3f8f527f559f11a471e91f0da6f&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=&amp;key=90cb886f1cc7938ce02286d16e1d45c7f8bd8c8e6628c7cce09fd9b0adb07af829f5664b6a8148e36c00af1c198cef2713b2546ceae6957072358daf234d9ebdef2f54cb80e1f8779f63dfa7c819feb9&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=vYTRuY4wEDzOu%2FtM7hkTZpLUAXt%2FdExH3GTHlFGB%2B7LxY6joxphtgRs97KOD%2B3Ji\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>联通昨天公布旗下的 5G 品牌名称为 “5Gⁿ”，并发布了品牌 Logo 和 Slogan“让未来生长”。</b></a> 品牌 Logo 将小写字母 n 放置于 5G 右上角，联通赋予 “n” 多种内涵，包括 number（数字）、near（距离）、more（更多可能，是因为两个 n 连在一起么）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122645GoZzCnjrhkiONv1T.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.642593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904241227272YhTgp9tqJQDI8C4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><p line=\"s4Ag\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUzNDQ3NTMyNw==&amp;mid=2247506789&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=cfe54ec0182d02060a5f05757ef4a6b5&amp;chksm=fa96bc35cde13523ad81979c148c3e0bcb6593393f59f49994389d5459c2b9ace0019f103104&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0424fFdoojluQ9SjjRNSqVU4&amp;key=579ba6bfe709a41a836b9d24a73dd7fddf445fd8cb28af873b845bc48a4f8555890170375532dcb0ae2ec820c6e0f4fb3ae3c4650f8b1cc32f2c823922ff0217c875512605d86c10cb747c2b74c720f6&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=vYTRuY4wEDzOu%2FtM7hkTZpLUAXt%2FdExH3GTHlFGB%2B7LxY6joxphtgRs97KOD%2B3Ji\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">今日头条推出“复联线索卡”活动。</a></b>今日头条在北京望京、国贸、海淀知春路和三里屯散落了数千张信息卡，线索卡涵盖了漫威电影的各种隐藏信息和彩蛋。参与者找到后可前往三里屯 3·3 广场参加复联主题粉丝体验展。今日头条 App 内还上线了一个<a href=\"https://i.snssdk.com/market/avengers/wap/index/?tt_from=weixin&amp;utm_source=weixin&amp;utm_medium=toutiao_ios&amp;utm_campaign=client_share&amp;wxshare_count=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">复联冷知识挑战赛。</a></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122740UWJ5RyKXm6TOLY8N.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122741e2wFIQYDEnLvUKR3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122741qG1Te6AfEmOBycx2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.075549\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122741BUq78sphGRHwauQl.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"jpzw\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA4NzAxMDk2Mg==&amp;mid=2651939411&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=5f7d0fb1de71ab480100e400612d3876&amp;chksm=8bda39aebcadb0b852cd8dd5c217d3e69c8671474e9312c3a89cbda2a924d1884543474e6864&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=&amp;key=e26fe09897582c58ac8c7925704c4e82f87ca4c3ed39adea2999d9063b5c126833aaf0257cc17cb87ece4b6b05407711fe9b662b4d0fef573ec478c5ddad57fcb483629c7611092d4045e06dc163f4b1&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=vYTRuY4wEDzOu%2FtM7hkTZpLUAXt%2FdExH3GTHlFGB%2B7LxY6joxphtgRs97KOD%2B3Ji\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雀巢将要开家“京味儿”快闪咖啡店。 </b></a>“北京感·感 CAFÉ” 咖啡厅落地在充满现代感的四合院中，现场提供的咖啡加入了老北京传统食物元素，比如驴打滚、艾窝窝、山楂糕甚至是二锅头。快闪<span style=\"-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">活动时间为 4 月 27 日至 5 月 5日。</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904241228030TCaFXYW4lipRqxK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.413889\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122803Hmyv9rxXkQDi1Y0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122803t23pP9ULBqnhAHuo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.412963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122829kBy4jK5vNfxEtAo1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201904241228034lqE0pynfLtN2zco.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.414815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122804rKXRzY9Pg1EiqVQo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.329630\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"QLaZ\"><b>Nike 最近要推出新鞋款，谍照释出方式蛮有意思。</b>几位运动员的鞋子都用🔥和 🤫 表情遮挡起了新鞋款。日本中长跑运动员 Suguru Osako 也在<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/suguru_osako/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Instagram </a>上发布了自己穿着新鞋的照片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122857TKvcAe5xD0nMYyC1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.249417\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122901CRwpraxe5cA2tIBM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122900h5FUug68v7GCAb2o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.239669\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424122857bNJcGeaT4RAP8OSK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662963\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"cso8\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T-FbFuS_mxU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>孩之宝的新广告 <em>Todos Podemos Cuidar</em>（我们都可以照顾）很可爱。</b></a>片中男孩和女孩一样都可以轻松上手孩之宝的  Baby Alive 娃娃，在玩具中学着如何照顾和关心其他人。品牌传递洋娃娃不单是女孩的专属玩具，试着消除玩具针对单一性别的观念。创意代理商是奥美/巴西。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"http://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=c0863o3zw7h\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"RRuQ\"><a href=\"http://controlpublicidad.com/campanas-publicitarias/audi-quiere-electrificar-la-revolucion-de-la-movilidad/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奥迪最新的 e-tron 电动车活动中，点亮了三幅版画。</b></a>内容主题分别是法国大革命、俄国革命运动和女权运动，寓意奥迪新款车型的出现也将成为电力革命的标志性事件。代理商是 DDB/西班牙。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424123020NSRizOLnJeQFm2j5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424123036GykB9x80nbHiupZW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190424123019OBtXJ0MHioyqWrGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.645161\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"xfG0\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/7085369226/4364171384174476\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>苹果昨天开通官方微博 “Apple 支持”，</b></a>借此渠道向用户直接提供使用技巧和技术支持。虽然目前一共也就发了 3 条微博，评论区大部分的实质性技术问题，苹果都给出回复。此外，苹果还有一个没更新过的微博账号 shotoniphone。</p><p line=\"r5VR\">题图来自：<a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/e31ANd1PXUw?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tyler Lastovich</a> on <a href=\"https://unsplash.com/search/photos/apple?utm_source=unsplash&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_content=creditCopyText\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Unsplash</a></p>"}